2002-0291 (La. 10/25/02)

STATE of Louisiana v. Oliver JARREAU. No. 2002-K-0291. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re Jarreau, Oliver; — Defendant; Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review, Parish of Orleans, Criminal District Court Div. H, No. 403-391; to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Circuit, No. 2000-KA-2013.

Denied.

JOHNSON, J., would grant the writ.
